@startuml
title Quick Request -> Clarification -> Team Blueprint Product Flow

actor Human
rectangle "Squadrail UI" {
  rectangle "Quick Request" as QuickRequest
  rectangle "Inbox / Issue Thread" as Inbox
  rectangle "Team Builder" as TeamBuilder
}

rectangle "Control Plane" {
  rectangle "PM Intake" as Intake
  rectangle "Clarification Policy" as Clarify
  rectangle "Projection / Dispatch" as Projection
  rectangle "Blueprint Registry" as Blueprint
  rectangle "Bulk Provisioning" as Provision
}

rectangle "Execution Org" {
  rectangle "PM" as PM
  rectangle "TL" as TL
  rectangle "Engineer" as Eng
  rectangle "Reviewer / QA" as Review
}

Human --> QuickRequest : short structured request
QuickRequest --> Intake : create intake root
Intake --> PM : assign root
PM --> Clarify : detect ambiguity
Clarify --> Inbox : question card
Human --> Inbox : short answer
Inbox --> Projection : answer + resume
Projection --> TL : execution-ready root / work items
TL --> Eng : assign implementation
Eng --> Review : submit for review
Review --> Human : only if decision needed

TeamBuilder --> Blueprint : preview blueprint
Blueprint --> Provision : apply team template
Provision --> PM
Provision --> TL
Provision --> Review

note right of Blueprint
v1 blueprints:
- small_delivery_team
- standard_product_squad
- delivery_plus_qa
end note

@enduml
